<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 1: HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">New Farm</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Real Estate Agent<br/><em style="color:#f5d07a;">New Farm.</em>
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Specialist property sales in New Farm and Brisbane's premium inner city.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/property-worth" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's Your Property Worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">One of Brisbane's most desirable addresses.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      New Farm consistently ranks among Brisbane's most sought-after suburbs. Riverside parks, character Queenslanders, a strong cafe culture and easy city access make it a perennial favourite with discerning buyers.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Properties in New Farm attract highly motivated, well-qualified buyers. My role is to build the right campaign, create genuine competition between them, and ensure that competition translates into the strongest possible result.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Brunswick Street is the spine of one of Brisbane's most vibrant eating and entertainment precincts, and buyers who discover it quickly understand why New Farm property has outperformed the Brisbane average over multiple cycles. New Farm Park's river frontage and the Powerhouse performance venue add cultural and recreational dimensions that affluent buyers place real weight on. Premium apartments along the river have attracted substantial interstate and overseas buyer interest as Brisbane's international profile has grown ahead of 2032. The suburb's tight supply of original character Queenslanders means that well-presented homes consistently clear auction with multiple registered bidders.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">New Farm Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Premium Inner City</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">High Demand Suburb</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Top buyer motivation</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/teneriffe" style="color:#c4912a;">Teneriffe</a>, <a href="/suburbs/kangaroo-point" style="color:#c4912a;">Kangaroo Point</a>, <a href="/suburbs/fortitude-valley" style="color:#c4912a;">Fortitude Valley</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
