      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Newstead</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Riverside precinct with strong growth momentum</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">East Brisbane</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560; line-height:1.6;">Walkable inner-city living with character homes</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:1.75rem;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.15rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Kangaroo Point</p>
