<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding:80px 24px; text-align:center;">
  <div style="max-width:700px; margin:0 auto;">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#f2efe9; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Thinking of selling in New Farm?</h2>
